                <zone fixed-size='210' forceUpdate='true' h='28255' id='20' is-fixed='true' type-v2='text' w='49414' x='50000' y='70703'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10' underline='true'>Key Findings</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>Approximately 24% of customers require immediate retention attention. Customers with 3+ products represent the highest-risk segment, while Active Members remain the most loyal group.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>Product ownership is the strongest churn driver, followed by senior age, low balances, and inactive membership status.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10' underline='true'>Recommendations</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>Focus retention efforts on high-value customers requiring immediate action through targeted offers and proactive engagement.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>Special attention should be given to customers with multiple products, inactive members, low balances, and poor credit scores to reduce future attrition and improve customer lifetime value.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
              </zone>
            </zone>
