                      <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                      <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    </zone-style>
                  </zone>
                </zone>
                <zone fixed-size='247' h='26953' id='25' is-fixed='true' layout-strategy-id='distribute-evenly' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98828' x='586' y='72005'>
                  <zone forceUpdate='true' h='26953' id='26' type-v2='text' w='49414' x='586' y='72005'>
                    <formatted-text>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>Key Findings</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>• Estimated revenue at risk from churned customers exceeds </run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>$186M</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>.</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>• Churned customers maintain an average balance of approximately </run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>$91K</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>.</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>• Over </run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>1,200 high-value customers</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'> have been lost.</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>• Low-balance customers show the highest churn rate (</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>35%</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>).</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>• Salary level has minimal impact on churn behavior.</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>• Customers with poor credit scores exhibit the highest churn rate (23.73%).</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>• Product ownership remains a strong churn indicator. </run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    </formatted-text>
                    <zone-style>
                      <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                      <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                      <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
                      <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    </zone-style>
                  </zone>
                  <zone forceUpdate='true' h='26953' id='27' type-v2='text' w='49414' x='50000' y='72005'>
                    <formatted-text>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>Recommendation</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='11'>Focus retention efforts on high-value customers before attrition   occurs. Implement proactive monitoring for customers with declining  engagement, poor credit scores, and high account balances. Revenue protection initiatives should prioritize segments contributing the greatest financial risk to the bank. </run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    </formatted-text>
                    <zone-style>
                      <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                      <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                      <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
                      <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    </zone-style>
                  </zone>
                </zone>
              </zone>
